data.description: Gorgeous home with Pool on quiet street in desirable Summer Creek Ranch! Open concept perfect for entertaining has spacious kitchen with granite counters, bar seating, sunny morning room & serving buffet. Downstairs has formal dining, casual living with gas fireplace, and a formal living that can also serve as a study. Master en suite overlooking pool has jet tub, dual vanities & walk in closet. Winding stairwell leads to 4 beds up with direct bath access & walk in closets. Upstairs find two more living areas. Chlorine play pool, fenced yard, shed & spacious covered patio are great for entertaining. Huge garage. Neighborhood boasts water park, pools, splash pad, playgrounds & more! Newer Roof & Fireplace 2016.
